NetModem/32 — Authors and Credits
=================================

Original author
---------------
Dedrick Allen (Allen Software)
  - NetModem/32 v2.0, the virtual COM port / FOSSIL driver and Telnet server.
  - Copyright (C) 1997-2001 Dedrick Allen / Allen Software.
  - Released under the GNU General Public License v2.
  - Original contact of record: drip@cris.com / http://www.allensoftware.com
    (historical; likely no longer active)

Recovery and revival
--------------------
  - Driver source recovered from the Ecstasy BBS (xtcbox.org) forum database
    backup, where Dedrick originally released it.
  - Original GUI blueprint recovered from the NetModem/32 v2.0 alpha-3 installer.
  - Revival: new Free Pascal / Lazarus GUI, replacing the original proprietary
    ShortcutBar component so the project builds entirely from free tools.

If you are Dedrick Allen, or know how to reach him, we'd be glad to credit or
hand over as he prefers. This project preserves his work under the license he chose.

Source provenance:
  Dedrick Allen  - original NetModem/32 author
  mag69          - gave the NetModem source code to the maintainer (made the revival possible)
  Antonio Rico (Reapern66 / verta1878) - revival maintainer
